family: Monoton

designer: Vernon Adams

approved: true
description: <p>Monoton is a contemporary take \
  on metalpress fonts like, for example, 'Prisma' \
  (originally designed in 1931 by Rudolf Koch.) \
  Monoton is a pure display webfont designed to \
  be used at font sizes above 30 points. Monoton \
  has been designed to be used freely across the \
  internet by web browsers on desktop computers, \
  laptops and mobile devices.</p>
  
